node.text:
Hold on to your butts, Gamers! @Qualcomm recently announced the Smartphone for Snapdragon Insiders, designed by Asus, featuring Snapdragon Elite Gaming which means all the speed you need for elite gamers everywhere. One of the Snapdragon 888 5G Mobile Platform highlights is the Qualcomm Adreno 660 GPU for 35% faster graphics rendering, true 10-bit color HDR, and the first mobile platform with Variable Rate Shading for 30% greater resolutions, higher frame rates, and low power requirements.
 
Be a part of the @SnapdragonInsiders community to get behind-the-scenes access and enter for a chance to win a special edition smartphone made JUST for Snapdragon Insiders! Join at SnapdragonInsiders.com #QualcommPartner

node.title: Snapdragon Elite Gaming on the Smartphone for Snapdragon Insiders

node.text:
Early look at the NEW Jordan 36 from @Jumpman23! 

Lighter & breathable w/ its all-new Jacquard Leno-Weave Upper you can 👀 right through it! 

Double stack Zoom Air in the front to take off. 

Gold chain on the heel reps 6 links for 6 rings & MJ's chain. 

The cutout on the bottom of the outer sole is to remove weight while being shaped like the tongue cutout on the Jordan 6.

Lace shroud cover calls out the 6 too.

The Scoop wing on the upper heel side is another call out to the Jordan 6 as well. 🔥🔥🔥

I've been a 34 guy. Can't wait to go 36! Thanks Jordan Brand! 🙏 Available Now! $185

#jumpman #jordan @nike @nikebasketball #airjordan #nike #basketball #ballislife #sneakers #nicekicks #kicksonfire

node.text:
Indulge me...#ShangChi filled my heart. ❤️ The story, the family, reppin' the Bay Area, reppin' for Asians AND Asian-Americans. The first FREAKIN ASIAN @MarvelStudios Superhero/Superheroine on film! It's a legit kick-ass movie with SO many laughs. The Soundtrack is 🔥 too.

There is now a generation of young people...and older... who see their own face on screen as #Marvel Superheroes. The power that holds will reverberate for generations to come.

THANK YOU @Marvel Cast & Crew! @simuliu @ronnychieng @michelleyeoh_official @zhang_meng_er @awkwafina @destinconrad @andyparkart @shangchi 🙏 So Proud.

Hold on to your butts, Gamers! @Qualcomm recently announced the Smartphone for Snapdragon Insiders, designed by Asus, featuring Snapdragon Elite Gaming which means all the speed you need for elite gamers everywhere. One of the Snapdragon 888 5G Mobile Platform highlights is the Qualcomm Adreno 660 GPU for 35% faster graphics rendering, true 10-bit color HDR, and the first mobile platform with Variable Rate Shading for 30% greater resolutions, higher frame rates, and low power requirements.
 
Be a part of the @SnapdragonInsiders community to get behind-the-scenes access and enter for a chance to win a special edition smartphone made JUST for Snapdragon Insiders! Join at SnapdragonInsiders.com #QualcommPartner
